## 7. Session Pitfalls

1. TLA+ `(*)` inside block comments — premature close
2. Non-short-circuit `/\ ` — CHOOSE on empty set
3. `{}` not a function — DOMAIN error on empty function
4. Double primed-variable — dead actions
5. TLC state explosion — 183M+ states with explicit clock
6. CFG function constants — parser rejects `[k|->v]`
7. Record with string keys — use `[x \in S |-> CASE ...]` instead of `["k"|->v]`
8. SUBSET of large sets — use small CONSTANT sets for PolicyRecord
9. `\ *` vs `\*` — space between `\` and `*` confuses parser
